cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software in research or write about it, please cite as below."
title: "obsidian-second-brain"
abstract: >
  A 31-command Claude Code skill that turns any Obsidian vault into a living
  AI-first second brain. Includes vault management, thinking tools, scheduled
  agents, and a research toolkit that pulls live X posts, Perplexity web
  research, and YouTube transcripts directly into vault notes. Vault notes
  follow a strict AI-first design rule optimized for future-Claude retrieval
  rather than human reading.
